146
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:12,148
Už má svoja roky, tak...

147
00:10:12,815 --> 00:10:13,608
Vtedy...

148
00:10:16,152 --> 00:10:17,403
Nemohlo to byť ono, však?

149
00:10:18,195 --> 00:10:18,738
Mai-chan?

150
