Čo sa deje? Vyzeráš utrápene.

151
00:10:21,866 --> 00:10:23,951
Je skoro ráno. Vstávaj.

152
00:10:24,118 --> 00:10:25,369
Mala by som?

153
00:10:25,620 --> 00:10:26,746
Veď už som hore.

154
00:10:27,204 --> 00:10:28,622
Obed v kaviarni, hej?

155
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:30,583
Jansé, prídem s Mikoto.

156
00:10:31,584 --> 00:10:32,668
Sadnite si.

157
00:10:33,377 --> 00:10:35,796
Áno, je to ich robota.

158
00:10:36,380 --> 00:10:38,632
Naši spoločníci zametajú stopy.

159
00:10:39,508 --> 00:10:42,761
Ale Sawada nemal veru veľa šťastia..

160
00:10:43,387 --> 00:10:48,058
Ale vyzerá to, že v nemocnici oňho bude dobre postarané.

161
00:10:48,893 --> 00:10:49,602
Čo bolo s Oufanom?

162
00:10:49,852 --> 00:10:50,728
Neviem.

163
00:10:50,978 --> 00:10:51,645
Ale...

164
00:10:52,438 --> 00:10:55,357
je tu dôkaz o boji.

165
00:10:55,816 --> 00:10:56,817
Je to nová HiME.

166
00:10:59,028 --> 00:10:59,153
Áno. Rozumiem.

167
00:11:05,701 --> 00:11:06,785
Urobím nejaký čaj.

168
00:11:07,036 --> 00:11:08,537
Prosím, odpočiň si.

169
00:11:16,587 --> 00:11:18,088
Aj keď tu ide o osud HiME

170
00:11:19,506 --> 00:11:23,177
nesmieme poľaviť.

171
00:11:27,598 --> 00:11:29,600
Hej, čo sa deje?

172
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:32,060
Čo?

173
00:11:34,646 --> 00:11:36,648
Hej, Mikoto, nechceš nejaké?

174
00:11:37,816 --> 00:11:38,442
Zjem ju.

175
00:11:40,777 --> 00:11:41,194
Mai.

176
00:11:42,529 --> 00:11:43,488
Môžeme ho navštíviť.

177
00:11:43,989 --> 00:11:46,199
Okej, budeme zástupkyne dievčat.

178
00:11:46,825 --> 00:11:49,119
A Tate a ja budeme reprezentovat chlapcov.

179
00:11:49,453 --> 00:11:50,912
Pred chvíľou som ho videl, tamto.

180
00:11:51,204 --> 00:11:53,331
No, tiež povedz ostatným, a...

181
00:11:54,499 --> 00:11:58,170
Zmeňme tému, má Tokiha-san mladšieho brata, alebo
niekoho takého?

182
00:12:00,797 --> 00:12:02,090
Volá s Takumi.

183
00:12:03,091 --> 00:12:05,802
Potom je to pravda.
Nečudujem sa, že tak tvrdo pracuje.

184
00:12:06,595 --> 00:12:07,512
Čo tým myslíš?

185
00:12:07,971 --> 00:12:08,638
No, vieš...

186
00:12:10,849 --> 00:12:11,766
Takumi-kun je?

187
00:12:23,486 --> 00:12:24,070
Kvety,

188
00:12:24,362 --> 00:12:25,113
ovocie,

189
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:26,239
a studený čaj.

190
00:12:26,322 --> 00:12:26,948
Správne?

191
00:12:27,198 --> 00:12:28,575
A čiastka za dopravu.

192
00:12:31,828 --> 00:12:32,954
Takže sme dohodnuté.

193
00:12:33,580 --> 00:12:35,165
Hej, máte dnes voľno?

194
00:12:35,832 --> 00:12:38,001
Mohli by sme dakde ísť.

195
00:12:38,543 --> 00:12:41,171
Čo vy na to? Toľko som toho zmeškala....

196
00:12:43,464 --> 00:12:44,132
Prepáč.

197
00:12:44,465 --> 00:12:46,551
Som trochu...

198
00:12:47,218 --> 00:12:48,803
Oh, jasné.

199
00:12:49,178 --> 00:12:51,139
Je nám to veľmi ľúto, Mai.

200
00:12:51,931 --> 00:12:54,267
Nie, spýtala som sa dosť zhurta.

201
00:12:54,809 --> 00:12:55,601
Je to v poriadku.

202
00:12:55,935 --> 00:12:56,185
Hej?

203
00:13:00,314 --> 00:13:06,446
Dneska majú Aoi a ostatní svoj program.

204
00:13:07,071 --> 00:13:09,416
Je to výborný film, mám naň dva lístky.
Poďme, lebo ich vypredajú.

205
00:13:10,241 --> 00:13:10,992
Počkajte.

206
00:13:12,368 --> 00:13:14,203
Je to paráda, mať od práce na deň pokoj.

207
00:13:14,704 --> 00:13:16,747
Ale aj tak nieje čo robiť.

208
00:13:19,584 --> 00:13:20,877
Myslím že pôjdem domov.

209
00:13:53,534 --> 00:13:55,786
Nebudem sa do toho miešať.

210
00:14:05,879 --> 00:14:06,880
Prečo?

211
00:14:08,465 --> 00:14:09,008
Dokelu.

212
00:14:17,433 --> 00:14:18,934
Sledujte autobus, prosím.

213
00:14:19,518 --> 00:14:20,102
Autobus?

214
00:14:20,144 --> 00:14:20,477
Áno.

215
00:14:20,936 --> 00:14:22,938
Vezmite ma, kam až sa dá.

216
00:14:33,073 --> 00:14:34,533
Tam je.

217
00:14:40,581 --> 00:14:41,623
Pani, váš výdavok.

218
00:14:41,832 --> 00:14:42,499
A vaša batožina!

219
00:15:09,985 --> 00:15:10,819
Ten netvor.

220
00:15:11,236 --> 00:15:12,404
Čo to bolo?

221
00:15:18,576 --> 00:15:19,160
Kuga-san.

222
00:15:19,244 --> 00:15:20,870
Doprdele, utiekol.

223
00:15:25,083 --> 00:15:26,376
Sú celkom rýchli. Ako som čakala.

224
00:15:27,043 --> 00:15:27,460
Poďme.

225
00:15:28,628 --> 00:15:29,129
Pohni si.

226
00:15:39,639 --> 00:15:41,182
Kto sú tí muži?

227
00:15:41,850 --> 00:15:44,602
Sú z organizácie nazvanej First District.

228
00:15:45,353 --> 00:15:46,896
Privádzajú do akadémie HiME.

229
00:15:51,276 --> 00:15:53,611
Zdravotníci sú falošní.
Odvezú pacientov do svojej nemocnice,

230
00:15:54,112 --> 00:15:56,698
kde im odstránia spomienky na to, čo videli.

231
00:16:01,285 --> 00:16:03,162
Žartuješ, však?

232
00:16:03,913 --> 00:16:06,833
Neviem, čo si myslíš o svojich schopnostiach,

233
00:16:07,667 --> 00:16:08,584
ale toto je realita.

234
00:16:09,335 --> 00:16:11,045
Pre nás, HiME.

235
00:16:16,759 --> 00:16:18,636
Yukimidai 4 je tiež preč?

236
00:16:18,845 --> 00:16:19,804
O tom nič neviem.

237
00:16:20,847 --> 00:16:21,180
Hej.

238
00:16:22,557 --> 00:16:23,683
Hej, ste zranená?

239
00:16:25,393 --> 00:16:26,143
Ste v poriadku?

240
00:16:28,145 --> 00:16:28,938
Jeden zranený.

241
00:16:49,417 --> 00:16:50,501
Hej, ty si...

242
00:16:52,128 --> 00:16:53,420
Čaute všetci.

243
00:16:53,879 --> 00:16:54,880
Tokiha-san.

244
00:16:57,132 --> 00:17:01,929
Nepovedali ste jej, že ideme navštíviť pána Sawadu?

245
00:17:02,179 --> 00:17:04,765
Pozbierali sme peniaze od každého v triede.

246
00:17:05,266 --> 00:17:06,850
